# Ignore all files that start with a dot, except for tracked dotfiles
.*
!.gitignore
!.gitignore_global

# Track Claude Code project-level subagent definitions and CLAUDE.md.
# These overrides also defeat the global ~/.gitignore rules of `.claude/*`
# and `CLAUDE.md`.
!.claude/
!.claude/agents/
!.claude/agents/*.md
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/skills
!CLAUDE.md

specs/*
